author: Graphic Designer 2
title: Jennings wins wild one over Lake Arthur
text: Jennings wins wild one over Lake Arthur By DYLAN BROSSETTE Daily News Sports Editor Touchdowns came in abundance and nary was any defense played Thursday night in Jerry Simmons Stadium, as the Jennings Bulldogs and Lake Arthur Tigers combined for 124 points and 1,057 yards of offense before back-to-back turnovers by the Tigers in the fourth quarter allowed the Dogs to pull away and secure a 68-56 victory.  //www.jenningsdailynews.net/?p=34227   Oct 2 2015.
